Personally, I had these type of zz world problems, with various medications like the three that I’ve named previously. These medications created a “zombie like” confusion and made me feel like I was in a void, but here’s the thing they also decreased my anxiety and allowed me to sleep through the night. Woe unto my family, when I would suddenly wake up in an angry sleep or would be a highly anxious person waking awake.

Aside from those situations, these downward drugs made me feel very lethargic and definitely unable to perform any amount of proper labour or dosage. It was suggest by my uppers (prescription doctor) that I should take these medications around dinner time. This type of medication will generally cost you in excess of $15.00 per bottle, which I would least way, average a one week stay, and of course all of this is depends on where you live and if you can afford it.
